<title>HUNGARY: Gardenia slips below subscription price.</title>
<headline>Gardenia slips below subscription price.</headline>
<dateline>BUDAPEST 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares in curtain maker Gardenia fell to 1,450 forints on Thursday, slipping below the 1,465 forints issue price for the first time since its listing on April 14, traders said.</p>
<p>Gardenia shares have moved mostly down in the past few days.</p>
<p>&quot;Gardenia has not dazzled investors since its listing despite a brief rally early on,&quot; one trader said.</p>
<p>At 1038 GMT Gardenia shares traded at 1,500 forints, down 230.</p>
<p>-- Budapest newsroom +36 1 327-4040</p>
